title: Capital Accounts: Other Capital Account Items: Reserve for Contingencies, Other Capital Accounts
notes:
This series is in the H.4.1 Factors Affecting Reserve Balances statistical press release and is available in FRED as WCPCA (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/WCPCA).

Authors: Cecilia Bao, Justin Chen, Nicholas Fries, Andrew Gibson, Emma Paine, and Kurt Schuler
